OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,FThe draft, entitled Ye Black-nebs By
OL,8,FName, features writing that Professor
OL,9,FGerard Carruthers, of the University
OL,10,Fof Glasgow's Centre for Studies,
OL,11,Fbelieves shows "implicit sympathy" for
OL,12,Fthe reformers.
OL,14,F"Black-nebs" was a term used to
OL,15,Fdescribe reformers in the 1790s, and
OL,16,Fis defined in the Dictionary of Scots
OL,17,FLanguage as meaning "one viewed as
OL,18,Fdisaffected to the government,
OL,19,Fespecially about the time of the
OL,20,FFrench Revolution and for some time
OL,21,Fafterwards".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
