OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1706220870
OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,FProf Carruthers said the early
OL,8,Fmanuscript, which was found among a
OL,9,Fcollection of Burns materials held at
OL,10,FBarnbougle Castle near Edinburgh, is
OL,11,F"the most explicit instance" of
OL,12,Fseveral where the Bard ostensibly
OL,13,Fwrote about history but actually had
OL,14,Fhis eye on 18th century current
OL,15,Faffairs.
OL,17,FHe believes Burns opted to keep the
OL,18,Fdraft under wraps out of concern the
OL,19,Fideas contained within it could put
OL,20,Fhis career as an exciseman for the
OL,21,FCrown at risk.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
