OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,FProf Carruthers said the discovery of
OL,8,Fthe early version of the song, which
OL,9,Fhas been released ahead of the Bard's
OL,10,Fbirthday on Thursday, provides "a
OL,11,Ffascinating insight" into his creative
OL,12,Fgenius.
OL,14,FHe explained: "The cancelled Ye Black-
OL,15,Fnebs chimes with other songs, most
OL,16,Ffamously Scots Wha Hae and A Man's A
OL,17,FMan For A' That', where revolutionary
OL,18,Fideas are smuggled in under the guise
OL,19,Fof writing about the Scottish wars of
OL,20,Findependence or universal brotherhood.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
