OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,F"In the end, Ye Black-nebs was more
OL,8,Fexplicit than these texts and is
OL,9,Fcompletely overwritten by Jacobite.
OL,11,F"Burns's original version, however,
OL,12,Fraises the strong possibility that the
OL,13,Ffinished version is code for more
OL,14,Frecent 1790s revolutionaries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
