OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,F"The variant Black-nebs
OL,8,F(revolutionaries) instead of Jacobites
OL,9,Fin the Barnbougle manuscripts
OL,10,Freferences someone of democratic
OL,11,Fprinciples following the French
OL,12,FRevolution and raises the intriguing
OL,13,Fproposition that Burns thought first
OL,14,Fof composing a lyric in the voice of a
OL,15,Fdisillusioned radical of 1790s before
OL,16,Fmoving from a Jacobin-themed to a
OL,17,FJacobite one.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
