OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,F"If Burns had lived longer, I believe
OL,8,Fhe would have been in favour of
OL,9,Fpolitical reforms emerging at that
OL,10,Ftime, particularly after the
OL,11,FNapoleonic wars of the early 1800s.
OL,13,F"He wouldn't have continued to use
OL,14,Fcunning to cover his allegiances, I
OL,15,Fdon't think. But at the time as a
OL,16,FCrown employee and at this point in
OL,17,Fhis life, he hadn't got there just yet.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
