OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1706220870
OL,3,CAxed Robert Burns manuscript could
OL,4,Chave put career in jeopardy, says
OL,5,Cscholar
OL,7,F"But I believe he would have
OL,8,Fincreasingly been on the side of
OL,9,Fdemocratic reform had he lived into
OL,10,Fthe early 19th century.
OL,12,F"However, when this was written,
OL,13,FEllisland, his farm, was not as
OL,14,Fproductive as he would have liked, and
OL,15,Fthings were uncertain financially for
OL,16,Fhim and his growing family.
OL,18,F"He was therefore dependent on his
OL,19,Fexcise employment and couldn't speak
OL,20,Fas freely as he might have liked."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
